    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for your dream ride? You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty \u2013 it\u2019s honestly in pristine, showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it looks and smells brand new. It drives like a total dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage. Seriously, you won't find a cleaner one out there! Come take a look and fall in love. Grab it before someone else does! \u2728",
