    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). This example features the high-revving 3.6L M96 flat-six paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic upgrade, ensuring mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut, utilizing factory-spec Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for optimal lateral grip. Zero bore scoring or oil consumption; the engine operates within tight factory tolerances. Inside, the cabin maintains its tactile integrity with supple leather and clear instrumentation. A turn-key investment for the discerning purist seeking peak analog feedback.",
      "price": 44800.0,
