    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle presents in showroom condition, having been meticulously pampered in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop as if it just rolled off the assembly line\u2014not a single swirl mark, stone chip, or blemish to be found. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats still retain that rich, new-car aroma and show zero signs of wear or creasing. Every button, screen, and dial functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records to prove its flawless upkeep. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of gentle use, it drives as tight and responsive as the day it was built. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a truly pristine example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
