      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one. It looks and drives just like it did the day I drove it off the lot. If you're looking for something that's basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'm happy to chat!",
